FRUIT AUCTION CO., Libelant Appellee, v. THE OWEGO, Her Engines, Boilers, etc.; United States of America, Claimant Appellant. (Consolidated Causes). (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. February 15, 1926.) No. 191. Joffe & Joffe, of New York City (Joseph Joffe, of New York City, of counsel), for appellee. Emory R. Buckner, U. S. Atty., of New York City (Horace M. Gray, Sp. Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for the United States.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree 11 F.(2d) 288, affirmed.
